---
import StatCounter from "~/components/react/StatCounter.tsx";
import ScrollReveal from "~/components/react/ScrollReveal.tsx";
---

<section class="border-b border-line">
  <div class="max-w-[1320px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 py-24 lg:py-36">
    <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-14 lg:mb-20">
      <div class="label">§ 01 — The shift</div>
      <div class="label hidden md:block">The food-safety reality</div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-y-16">
      <ScrollReveal client:visible className="lg:pr-10 lg:border-r lg:border-line">
        <div class="label mb-4">Time to result</div>
        <div
          class="stat-num text-[clamp(40px,4.5vw,64px)] font-medium num-tabular text-paper"
        >
          <span class="lt">&lt;</span><StatCounter client:visible target={15} /><span
            class="text-accent">min</span
          >
        </div>
        <p
          class="mt-6 text-paper/80 text-[16px] leading-relaxed max-w-[34ch]"
        >
          From sample to results in under fifteen minutes. Your operator does
          it. No lab, no shipping.
        </p>
      </ScrollReveal>

      <ScrollReveal
        client:load
        delay={120}
        className="lg:px-10 lg:border-r lg:border-line"
      >
        <div class="label mb-4">Recalls caused by Listeria &amp; Salmonella</div>
        <div
          class="stat-num text-[clamp(40px,4.5vw,64px)] font-medium num-tabular text-paper"
        >
          <StatCounter client:visible target={40} /><span class="text-accent">%</span>
        </div>
        <p
          class="mt-6 text-paper/80 text-[16px] leading-relaxed max-w-[34ch]"
        >
          Two bugs drive almost half of microbial food recalls. Both are still
          caught days late by the standard lab workflow.
        </p>
      </ScrollReveal>

      <ScrollReveal client:visible delay={240} className="lg:pl-10">
        <div class="label mb-4">Consumers who would stop buying</div>
        <div
          class="stat-num text-[clamp(40px,4.5vw,64px)] font-medium num-tabular text-paper"
        >
          <StatCounter client:visible target={68} /><span class="text-accent">%</span>
        </div>
        <p
          class="mt-6 text-paper/80 text-[16px] leading-relaxed max-w-[34ch]"
        >
          One recall is enough. Most shoppers walk and don't come back. The
          cost of catching it late is the customer.
        </p>
      </ScrollReveal>
    </div>

    <ScrollReveal client:visible delay={120}>
      <p
        class="mt-20 lg:mt-28 max-w-[58ch] text-[18px] lg:text-[20px] text-paper/75 leading-[1.55]"
      >
        Today, microbial testing means shipping samples to a lab and waiting
        two to four days. By the time the results come back, the product has
        usually already shipped. <span class="text-paper">We bring the test
        to the line</span>, so you catch contamination before it leaves the
        building.
      </p>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </div>
</section>
